{"tid":2514522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無玩開GTA既手足呀,想你幫手","createTime":"2021-05-03T10:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T12:26:01.000Z","uid":54517,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"27261f71240c90459b51c37819a343d2729bf24b","tid":2514522,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:04:41.000Z","msg":"邵家臻 <br />\n2分鐘  &middot; <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfPteRaCYPPd16RbpMojbQ73cQJJ1iNbYsNv8KZ38ENUA?filename=2zyYd4m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zyYd4m.png&h=b81ffe07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【為手足Someone寄打氣信】<br />\n上年今日，手足Someone被捕，於獄中度過呢個日子嘅佢，一定唔好受。<br />\n在此呼籲有心人為佢寄去打氣信，Someone喜歡玩GTA遊戲（又名：俠盜獵車手）、也喜歡睇《School Days》動畫（又名：日在校園），作為一個血氣方剛嘅中學生，佢亦會間中𥄫女（獄中嘅佢無法𥄫女了）。<br />\n佢係過目不忘小神童，同時也關心國際時事。<br />\n歡迎大家寄打氣信件給這位手足，將溫暖送到他手中。<br />\n<br />\n想你幫手加入做寫信師呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7aff829f88fb0b65e75da3e3c99acf4de667c3","tid":2514522,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:05:26.000Z","msg":"搵gay巴囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922c82e5fc394d0a7d2fdd604195fe5a132842c6","tid":2514522,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b7aff829f88fb0b65e75da3e3c99acf4de667c3","tid":2514522,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:05:26.000Z","msg":"搵gay巴囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:05:59.000Z","msg":"一個邊夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mous